## Attribution Requirements

When using this project or its derivatives:

1. **Keep this LICENSE file** intact in your project
2. **Credit the original author** (S540d) in your documentation
3. **Respect third-party licenses** - especially Spotify API Terms of Service
4. **Cover Art**: If you display album covers from Cover Art Archive, follow CC BY-NC-SA 3.0

## Spotify API Terms

This project uses the Spotify Web API. When deploying:

- You must comply with [Spotify Developer Terms of Service](https://developer.spotify.com/terms)
- You need your own Spotify Developer credentials
- Commercial use may have additional restrictions

## MusicBrainz Attribution

This project uses data from MusicBrainz. Please consider:

- MusicBrainz data is CC0 (public domain)
- Consider [donating to MusicBrainz](https://metabrainz.org/donate)
- Add attribution in your app (recommended but not required)

